instructions: In your web browser of choice, type in the address duo.google.com . Verify the phone number your Duo account is associated with by entering it on the screen. Click Get verification code . You will receive an SMS at the number you provided with a one-time code. Enter the one-time code on the screen.

In your web browser of choice, type in the address duo.google.com . Alternatively, you can make a Duo call on a Chromebook or Chromebox through the Duo app. Google Duo Web Call Source: Jeramy Johnson / Android Central Search for and/or choose a contact to call. Click Start call . Choose video or voice . Google Duo Web Call Source: Jeramy Johnson / Android Central When the call is over, select end call . Google Duo Web Call Source: Jeramy Johnson / Android Central
